Class DateList

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.fortuna.ical4j.model.DateList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<Date>, java.util.Collection<Date>, java.util.List<Date>

    public class DateList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.List<Date>, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<Date>
    $Id$ [23-Apr-2004] Defines a list of iCalendar dates. If no value type is specified a list defaults to DATE-TIME instances.
